latestPosts.caption:
Our founder, @jain.shubhika, has been testing GloTint on herself for over 2 years! 

Some days it was patchy, some days cakey.
Too much coverage made it look heavy, too little made it pointless.
She knew one thing: we needed something that looked like skin but gave you just enough coverage.

Because let’s be honest when your foundation makes your skin look older, drier, wrinklier…
What’s the point of spending ₹10,000 on something everyone knows is makeup?

We studied global formulas but they were too oily, too synthetic, no skincare, no SPF.

So we kept going.
We reduced the oiliness.
We made it waterproof (because life happens, you cry, you sweat, you live).
We added skincare: peptides, botanicals, hydration.
We made it sheer, breathable, glow-giving like your skin, but better.

GloTint wasn’t built in a lab overnight. It was built from AM to PM, through meetings, shoots, breakdowns and breakthroughs.

And now, it’s ready for your everyday life too!

GloTint. One bottle. Seven benefits.

Tint, foundation, serum, moisturizer, sunscreen, primer, and illuminator — all in one! ✨

Why layer 7 products when one does it all? 🥰

[Coming soon, New product, Product Launch, 7in1, GloTint]
